oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Stereograph image of cotton being unloaded from a cart in Memphis, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This stereocard shows cotton being unloaded from a mule drawn wagon onto the cobblestone landing in Memphis along the Mississippi river.
